These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, social-worker, journalist, nurse
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, apricot, avocado, grapefruit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, tennis, cycling
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, ebony, lilac, blue
1. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is between the journalist and the nurse##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who likes lilac is the journalist##1
7. the person eating apricot is on the left of the nurse##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
9. the social-worker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | social-worker | nurse   | electrician  | journalist  |
| Food   | apricot    | grapefruit    | asparagus      | avocado    |
| Sport   | cycling | golf | tennis | biathlon |
| Color     | blue  | black       | ebony    | lilac     |

