.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
City: hannover, colone, nizza, hamburg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, montecristo, game, tiparillo
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, mirinda, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, designer, teacher, engineer
1. the engineer is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the designer##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person drinking mirinda and the chef##2
6. the engineer is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person drinking lemonade##2
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
8. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
9. the game-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| City         | hamburg | colone    | nizza  | hannover    |
| Cigar   | siglo      | montecristo  | tiparillo  | game |
| Beverage           | lemonade      | mirinda       | juice      | soy-milk       |
| Job         | designer    | engineer | teacher | chef |

