.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, pink, azure, ebony
4 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, mouse, rabbit
House: tower, futuristic, farmhouse, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, january, april
1. the farmhouse house is the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the futuristic house is the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
8. the person who likes coral is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the rabbit##2
9. the owner of the mouse is between the person who likes azure and the futuristic house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color        | pink | azure     | coral   | ebony     |
| Pet       | turtle   | pony   | mouse | rabbit |
| House         | tower   | farmhouse | gothic-revival       | futuristic    |
| Birthday   | january    | november | october  | april    |

