 4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is the colonial house##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the tram and the wooden house##2
10. the cottage house is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
