.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goat, chinchilla, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, surfing, golf, cricket
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, roller, scooter
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, hip-hop, blues, reggae
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the fan reggae and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the fan rock is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the fan blues is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan reggae##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the fan blues##1
